snippet.title: Pinnacle Point - The Silence is Watching | Indie Horror Showcase
snippet.description:
Something feels off. The air is heavy, the silence watches… and the island isn't empty. You came here for answers, but it has other plans.

This is a look at my progress on Pinnacle Point, a psychological horror game where reality twists and the past refuses to stay buried. Expect eerie atmospheres, unsettling encounters, and a story that unfolds in layers of mystery and fear.

Follow along as the island reveals its secrets.
